data.description: Step into tranquility with this two-bed, one-bath main floor condo, a gem within the subdivision. Meticulously upgraded by the previous owner in 2021, revel in the allure of fresh paint, new carpet, vinyl plank flooring, upgraded light fixtures, and a new water heater. Experience the epitome of move-in readiness with in-unit laundry and included appliances, providing the ultimate convenience. Revel in the extra perk of reserved covered parking, conveniently located near the condo's entrance—no steps, just seamless accessibility. Don't miss your chance to own the best in the subdivision. Embrace the comfort, style, and ease of this upgraded condo - your sanctuary in the heart of South County living. Act now and make every day a celebration of your new home! HWA Diamond Home Warranty available.
